show.description: Supreme is a fantasy-romance tale of an aspiring hero’s journey to become a celestial master. He faces powerful enemies, overcomes mystical challenges, and discovers ancient secrets. Amidst it all, love blossoms, shaping his destiny in unexpected ways.
